data.description:
Welcome Home to Brookstone at Forest Lake. Our Fairview B (Lot 42) plan is a beautiful 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bath open concept home! The large foyer has crown molding and a coat closet! Upgraded luxury vinyl flooring on main level, laundry and baths. This home features upgraded Shaker-style cabinetry with crown and pull knobs. Energy Star stainless steel appliances, granite counters in kitchen and baths. Entertain family and friends around the large island equipped with an audio docking station w/ speakers, music port & USB charging ports. Carpeted bedrooms on 2nd level, w/laundry room. Standard features include a Moen kitchen faucet with sprayer, garbage disposal, clear shower door in owner's bath, 2-car garage with remotes, sprinkler system, R-50 insulation, advanced framing, durable Hardie Plank siding, 30 yr Architectural shingles and gutters! All of this and much more is nestled on a manicured lot in a gated community. STOCK PHOTOS! Brick in lieu of stone. 

Great Southern Homes is offering a $10,000 incentive for closing costs, prepaids, rate buy down and etc, with use of Homeowners Mortage on select homes that can close by the end of the year!  This home also qualifies for $10,000 in MAD MONEY, that can go towards closing cost or it can be taken off the sales price, WOW! 

*Est. Completion Date - Dec 2022 Model Open Daily 1449 Feldspar Ct. Mon. - Sat. 11am-6pm Sun. 1pm-6pm
